We’re always looking for committed and talented people who can join us in our journey to help make the local area – and the world – a little better.
Lediga tjänster
Make a difference at Malarenergi | Mälarenergi
We’re currently looking to fill the current positions.
Here at Mälarenergi, we’re always working to improve life for you and hundreds of thousands of other people in the Mälardalen region. Work that helps to make the local area, society – even the world – a little better. Our products and services form the basis for several crucial social functions, such as energy, water and broadband solutions.
We use an online recruitment system called Visma Recruit. Click on one of our job vacancies to find out more information about the position and to submit your application online. Our corporate language is Swedish and is often a prerequisite for managing certain tasks within our business.
Time to change the world – and your life?
Do you also want to make a difference?


SOURCE: https://www.malarenergi.se//kundcenter-privat/information-in-other-languages/english/about-malarenergi/
We offer career opportunities in many business areas. If you're interested in a career with Mälarenergi, check in with us here:
Switching electricity supplier is a simple and free process. If you want to switch to Mälarenergi, contact the Customer Centre helpline on 021 39 50 50 and we can help you.
About Mälarenergi | Mälarenergi
Mälarenergi provides electricity, district heating, water and broadband via Stadsnät, primarily in the Mälardalen region. We also sell electricity to domestic and business customers all over Sweden. Mälarenergi was established in 1861 and is 100% owned by the City of Västerås.
