My Pages (Mitt Mälarenergi) give you full control of your bills and your electricity consumption. You can also check your account whenever it suits you and take advantage of different offers.
You can log into Mitt Mälarenergi using Mobile Bank-ID if you have one. If not, please call our Customer Centre.
At Mitt Mälarenergi you can also register for free SMS or E-mail notifications in case of, for example, a power failure.
